{"tid":2408054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸新移民佔20%公屋申請 6%擬安排內地家屬來港定居","createTime":"2021-02-14T14:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T03:32:33.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9b1e752e72171a94b197cca1a147c33703d8ff34","tid":2408054,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"坊間不時有聲音批評公屋資源「被大陸人搶晒」。房委會調查發現，截至去年3月底，一般公屋申請者及其家人當中，有20%是居港少於7年的內地新來港人士，較2016年增加5個百分點。6%一般申請者有意安排內地家屬來港定居。而非長者單身申請者有11%已婚，部份人的配偶和子女由內地來港後，很可能轉為一般申請者。數據顯示，5%非長者單身申請者亦有意安排內地家屬來港定居。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/S2MXWKPPKJHUTLLNVXEH3I4NDM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2FS2MXWKPPKJHUTLLNVXEH3I4NDM%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=a3474817\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210209%2FS2MXWKPPKJHUTLLNVXEH3I4NDM%2F&h=49e56ab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210209/S2MXWKPPKJHUTLLNVXEH3I4NDM/</a>"},{"pid":"5a8bc04ed372e24fc2546927987394efe1f902fe","tid":2408054,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:46:00.000Z","msg":"點知20%咁少呀屌"},{"pid":"2859b9a5fef0f130c5f86ad2c7b2bac15ff13991","tid":2408054,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3128679b2fe01ab53c272ae70c80e569d8d468c4","tid":2408054,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"[TVB造馬風波] 蘋果：入錯電話？驗證咗電話號碼先有得抽利是！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2407957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\"